<A>__{she gestures to the black suitcase by her feet. he smiles and lifts it up on the table, unzipping it open. lying inside is a cool million, the thousand dollar bills are inside stacks of a hundred thousand each. at the sight of all this lettuce, budd lets out a whistle.}
