<D>__{"...its neurotoxic venom is one of nature's most effective poisons, acting on the nervous system causing paralysis. the venom of a black mamba can kill a human in four hours, if say bitten on the ankle or the thumb. however, a bite to the face or torso can bring death from paralysis within twenty minutes.}
<P>__{(up from paper to budd)}
<D>__{now you should listen to this cause this concerns you.}
